headline: Treasury Yields Fall as Bets on Fed Cut Increase
summary: Treasury yields declined ahead of October’s JOLTS report due at 10 a.m. ET. Odds of an interest-rate cut this month rose to 73% on the CME’s FedWatch tool, from 62% Monday.
